<div class="container">
    <div class="wrapper flow">
        <h3 class="center">Living the Dance</h3>
        <p>
            Come to a place where dance is lived.
        </p>
        <p>
            Where each day unfolds in rhythm, <br />
            and the body listens, as much as it moves.    
        </p>
        <p>
            At Nrityagram, practice becomes a way of being - <br />
            held gently by earth, time, and attention.
        </p>
        <br />
        <p>
            The Summer Workshop at Nrityagram is a residential immersion in the foundational principles of Odissi, as developed and practised within our community.
        </p>
        <p>
            More than a training programme, it offers a glimpse into a way of living, where practice, discipline, and daily life are inseparable.
        </p>
        <p>
            Here, dance is approached as a continuous, embodied inquiry - unfolding through rhythm, repetition, and attention.
        </p>
    </div>
</div>
<div class="container accent-bg">
    <div class="wrapper flow">
        <h1 class="center">Faculty</h1>
        <div class="image-plus top-flow">
            {% image "https://res.cloudinary.com/nrityagram/image/upload/v1742635687/surupa-pavi_q8a61i.jpg",
      "Nrityagram Resident Faculty: Guru Surupa Sen and Pavithra Reddy",
